  <brief_title>CREMS Prostate Biopsy Pain Relief Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pain Relief With Local Anesthetic at Time of Prostate Biopsy: Comparing Apical and Basal Injection Versus Basal Injection Alone</official_title>
